            <p>A.J. Celiano's pursuit of excellence in quality service, and the family tradition of honesty and integrity, has defined the company as a reputable and professional leader in the industry since our inception in 1925. Dedication to this philosophy in all arenas of business allows us to consistently exceed our customers' highest expectations.</p>
