            <p>A.J. Celiano, Inc. was founded in 1925 by Alfred J. Celiano and has been in continuous operation ever since. The history of A.J. Celiano, Inc. began with the dreams of Alfred and his devoted wife, Theresa. As a young man with a wealth of enthusiasm and imagination, A.J. laid the foundation for the company. The roots of this foundation are based on a commitment to three principles:<br></p>
