        <p>Inspired by his father’s dedication to these principles and passion for his work, A.J.’s son, Eugene R. Celiano, became the first of a new generation to build upon his foundation.  Eugene committed himself to the expansion of his father’s dream.  Today, the unique family legacy continues under the leadership and work of brothers Daniel, Gregory and Michael.  Yet another generation of succession has come when Thomas Celiano joined the company in 2007.  Together, they work collaboratively to continue the unyielding commitment and principles set for nearly a century ago.</p>    
